                              A L P H A                  
by Rev3n4nt  
===========================================================================
Advanced engine needed  : GZDoom 3.2.5 or newer
===========================================================================
Title                   : Faithful Doom (version 0.1a)
Filename                : FDoom01a.pk3
Release date            : December 29, 2018
Authors                 : 'Rev3n4nt' aka Farid Kemyakov
Email Address           : rev3n4nt@gmail.com
Other Files By Author   : FDoom01a_up2x.pk3

Additional Credits :
Agent_Ash - for Beautiful Doom and inspiration
Gifty - for Smooth Doom and inspiration
hidfan - Doom Neural Upscale 2X sprites & textures (not included)
Perkristian - smooth weapons animation sprites based upon)
Sergeant Mark IV - sprites and coding	
Z86 - spritework for weapons
Blox - spritework for weapons

Description :	Faithful Doom is mod with idea for keeping original doom sprites and adding ontop new frames only. 
Mod is made with keepng in mind, that 'Neural Upscale 2X' sprites & textures are for vanilla game. 
Optionally goes with pack with new frames for 'Neural Upscale 2X' - FDoom01a_up2x.pk3.

Known Issues :	Few wrong offsets in frames of: pistol, chaingun.

===========================================================================

 ** VERSIONS CHANGELOG **
---------------------------------
version 0.1a || December 29, 2018

* All weapons nested from vanilla & enhanced with additional animation frames
* Somw sprites have been redrawn, with better detail and some variations.
